{"type": "article", "id": 21350, "title": "故事耳环", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-27T07:30:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133914ziXrOZtSCJeYMlQT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 nendo 推出的一套耳环，一共有 12 组，每组 3 种，分别取自小鸟、树叶、蝴蝶、花朵、雪花等元素，很有童话故事的情景感，因而取名为“stories”。小巧的外形像是夹在书页里的书签，只有 0.5mm 厚度，是在不锈钢板上镀金或银制成。此外，这组耳环是夹在耳朵上的，无需穿孔，可以吸引更广泛的人群。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/small-stories-2/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150917kGI2m3z4cJaHhOoi.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150917N4mO6wqfZAsU5BdL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509183b4zpuSnmUrhdeRP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150918NdIVQCfaE3WxnFKh.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509193ZLiJVMlEpBadwnT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150919sK9GyMulHJPBAQoj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}